title: Artist Driven Asia Tour - Part Two: Hong Kong
description: Part Two of the Artist Driven Asia tour takes Pose, Vizie, and Steel to Hong Kong, where they link up with local artists Xeme and Sinic as they continue their adventure and search for inspiration over three days in the bustling metropolis.
